metadata.name: FashionFreak #001
metadata.description:
Fashion Freaks is the first collection by CNFT â€“ home for art and fashion, made up of 77 Fashion NFTs.
The collection covers all seasons from winter to summer, with each drop adding another item to your closet.
We created a collection that would go beyond the fourth dimension, away from a world where fashion narratives are lead by the top fashion houses.
In our dimension, there are no rules, we are not inmates imprisoned by the rules of fashion.
